OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy rain, occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy. Remaining cloudy through the
OL,8,Fearly hours with further spells of
OL,9,Frain although rain becoming patchy
OL,10,Flater. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,13,Foccasional rain, perhaps turning
OL,14,Fpersistent in the southeast for a
OL,15,Ftime. Brightening up in the afternoon
OL,16,Fwith heavy showers and a chance of
OL,17,Fthunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
